CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 29, 1957, pg. A16 reads: "Final Plans - The 3300 Club's social committee makes final plas [sic] for the lawn party and fashion show to be given June 30 on the lawn of 3377 Webster Ave. The house are from 4 until 7, and the commentator wil [sic] by Mrs. Toki Schalk Johnson.  Shown are Mrs. Alberta Williams, president; Mmesc. [sic] Cornelia Blair, Mary Edwards, Lillian Talley, Martha Milton, Missie Yates and Lois Spencer, chairman of the committee. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of social committee of 3300 Club, including Alberta Williams, Cornelia Blair, Mary Edwards, Lillian Talley, Martha Milton, Missie Yates, and Lois Spencer, gathered around coffee table for meeting
